data.description:
MOTIVATED SELLER ENTERTAINING ALL OFFERS
This 3BR 2BA Ranch sits on a spacious corner lot, on a quiet street, in an accessible neighborhood. Minutes from the expressway, restaurants, and shopping. 
This house has been well maintained and includes a roof, HVAC, Water Heater, and Furnace that have all been fully updated in the last 5-7years and a new upstairs floor that's just over a year old! This house boasts a full basement, perfect for entertaining. You'll fall in love with the amount of natural light that comes through the large window in the living room. Hurry and view before it's gone!
